name: ASCEND
description: A Phoenix rises from its ashes. Defeat is like ashes. You can ascend and shine with your brave soul. Falling apart doesn't make you weak — instead, you get to build new and better things. Ascend like a Phoenix. Don't let hatred destroy everything, like a burning tree in the forest. The love and caress of a kind soul will solve any problem. Let the light shine, even, it gets dark.
